<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
      xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
      metal:use-macro="context/@@engine/macros/page"
      i18n:domain="cc_org">
<head>
  <title metal:fill-slot="title">CC&empty;</title>


  <metal:headers fill-slot="headers">
    <base href="" tal:attributes="href string:${context/@@absolute_url}/zero/" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" 
	  href="http://yui.yahooapis.com/2.4.1/build/button/assets/skins/sam/button.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"
	  href="http://yui.yahooapis.com/2.4.1/build/container/assets/container.css">

<script type="text/javascript"
	src="ext-2.0/adapter/yui/yui-utilities.js"
	tal:attributes="src
	context/++resource++cc/ext-2.0/adapter/yui/yui-utilities.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript"
	src="ext-2.0/adapter/yui/ext-yui-adapter.js"
	tal:attributes="src
	context/++resource++cc/ext-2.0/adapter/yui/ext-yui-adapter.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript"
	src="ext-2.0/ext-all.js"
	tal:attributes="src
	context/++resource++cc/ext-2.0/ext-all.js"></script>

    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="zero.css"
	  tal:attributes="href context/++resource++cc/includes/zero.css" />

    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="ext-all.css"
	  tal:attributes="href
	  context/++resource++cc/ext-2.0/resources/css/ext-all.css" />

    <script src="zero_chooser.js" type="text/javascript"
       tal:attributes="src context/++resource++cc/includes/zero_chooser.js">
    </script>
  </metal:headers>

</head>

<body>

<metal:left fill-slot="sidebar">
</metal:left>

<metal:title fill-slot="page-header-title"></metal:title>

<metal:body fill-slot="body">
<div class="yui-skin-sam">

  <div id="zero-wizard">

    <div id="page-welcome" class="yui-module">
      <div class="hd">CC&empty;</div>
      <div class="bd">

	<p>
	  CC&empty; enables you to indicate that a work is free of copyright,
	  moral rights, database rights, and any other rights that might be
	  asserted, to the extent possible under law. Do you want to: 
	</p>

	<p class="indent">
	  <strong>Assert</strong> that a work is free of legal encumberances as a
	  matter of fact, e.g., because the
	  work <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Public_Domain#Expiration">is
	  old enough</a> to be in the public domain, or because the
	  work is in a class not protected by copyright such
	  as <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Copyright_status_of_work_by_the_U.S._government">U.S. government
	  works</a>.  Curators and publishers of public domain
	  material may be well placed to make such an assertion. You
	  may
	  <span id="radio2" class="yui-button yui-radio-button">
            <span class="first-child">
              <button type="submit" name="zero-type" value="assertion"
		      id="do-assertion">
                continue
              </button>
            </span>
	  </span>

	</p>

	<p>OR</p>

	<p class="indent">
	  <strong>Waive</strong> all rights that you have over a work. You can only do this if
	  you
	  hold <a href="http://wiki.creativecommons.org/Before_Licensing#Make_sure_you_have_the_rights">the
	  necessary rights for the work</a>. If you hold 
	  all of the necessary rights and want to grant the public the
	  right to use your work in any way with no restrictions or
	  requirements whatsoever, 
 	  <span id="radio1" class="yui-button yui-radio-button">
            <span class="first-child">
              <button type="submit" name="zero-type" value="waiver"
		      id="do-waiver">
                continue
              </button>
            </span>
	  </span>
	</p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div id="page-waiver" class="x-hide-display">


<metal:waiver define-macro="waiver-ui">

<div id="waiver_ui" class="yui-module">
  <div class="hd">CC&empty; Waiver</div>
  <div class="bd">
    <form id="form-waiver" action="confirm-waiver">
      <input type="hidden" name="zero-action" value="waiver" />
      <input type="hidden" name="license-uri"
	     value="http://labs.creativecommons.org/licenses/zero-waiver/1.0/us/" />

      <div class="form-row">
	<div class="form-question">Your name:</div>
	<div class="form-answer"><input name="name" class="form-field"/></div>
      </div>
      <div class="form-row">
	<div class="form-question">Your URL:</div>
	<div class="form-answer"><input name="actor_href"
					class="form-field"/>
	</div>
      </div>

      <div class="form-row">
	<div class="form-question">Title of your work:</div>
	<div class="form-answer"><input name="work_title" class="form-field"/></div>
      </div>

      <div class="form-row">
	<div class="form-question">URL of your work:</div>
	<div class="form-answer"><input name="work_url" class="form-field"/></div>
      </div>

      <div class="form-row">
	<div class="form-question">
	  <input name="confirm" type="checkbox"
	  id="confirm_waiver" class="form-field"
	  value="waiver" />
	</div>
	<div class="form-answer">
	  <label for="confirm">I hereby waive all rights to this work. 
	    To the extent possible 
	    under the law, I waive all copyright, moral rights, database
	    rights, and any other rights that might be asserted over the
	    work.
	  </label>
	</div>
      </div>

      <div class="form-row">
	<div class="form-question">&nbsp;</div>
	<div class="form-answer">
	  <input type="submit" id="waiver-submit" 
		 name="field1" value="continue"> 
	</div>
      </div>

    </form>

    <br clear="both"/>&nbsp;
  </div>
</div>
</metal:waiver>


    </div>

    <div id="page-assertion" class="x-hide-display">

<metal:assertion define-macro="assertion-ui">

<div id="assertion_ui" class="yui-module">
  <div class="hd">CC&empty; Assertion</div>
  <div class="bd">
    <form id="form-assertion" action="confirm-assertion">
      <input type="hidden" name="zero-action" value="assertion" />
      <input type="hidden" name="license-uri"
	     value="http://labs.creativecommons.org/licenses/zero-assert/1.0/us/" />

      <div class="form-row">
	<div class="form-question">Your name:</div>
	<div class="form-answer"><input name="name" class="form-field" /></div>
      </div>

      <div class="form-row">
	<div class="form-question">Your URL:</div>
	<div class="form-answer"><input name="actor_href"
					class="form-field"/>
	</div>
      </div>

      <div class="form-row">
	<div class="form-question">Title of the work:</div>
	<div class="form-answer"><input name="work_title" class="form-field"/></div>
      </div>

      <div class="form-row">
	<div class="form-question">URL of the work:</div>
	<div class="form-answer"><input name="work_url" class="form-field"/></div>
      </div>

      <div class="form-row">
	<div class="form-question">
	  <p>I assert that this work is free of any copyrights because:
	  </p>
	</div>
	<div class="form-answer">
	  <input name="assertion_reason" type="checkbox" class="reason"
		 value="us_govt" />
	  <label>the work was created by the
	  U.S. Government.</label> <br/>

	  <input name="assertion_reason" type="checkbox" class="reason" 
		 value="pd" />
	  <label for="pd">the work was created in the US before 1923.</label> <br/>

	  <input name="assertion_reason" type="checkbox" class="reason" 
		 value="other" />
	  <label for="other">other.</label> <br/>
	</div>
      </div>

      <div class="form-row">
	<div class="form-question">&nbsp;</div>
	<div class="form-answer">
	  <input type="submit" id="assertion-submit" name="field1" 
		 value="continue"> 
	</div>
      </div>

    </form>
    <br clear="both"/>&nbsp;
  </div>

</metal:assertion>

    </div>

    <div id="page-waiver-confirmation" class="x-hide-display">

<metal:confirm-waiver define-macro="confirm-waiver">
      <div id="confirm-waiver" class="yui-module">
	<div class="hd">Confirm CC&empty; Waiver</div>
	<div class="bd">

	    <p>Are you certain you wish to waive all rights to your
	      work?  Once these rights are waived, you can not reclaim
	      them. 
	    </p>

	    <div class="form-row yui-buttongroup">
	      <span class="yui-button">
		<span class="first-child">
		  <button type="submit" id="decline-waiver-submit"
			  name="decline">
		    No, I Don't Waive
		  </button>
		</span>
	      </span>

	      <span class="yui-button">
		<span class="first-child">
		  <button type="submit" id="confirm-waiver-submit" 
			  name="confirm">
		    Yes, I Waive
		  </button>
		</span>
	      </span>
	    </div>

	</div>
      </div>
</metal:confirm-waiver>

    </div>

    <div id="page-assertion-confirmation" class="x-hide-display">

<metal:confirm-assertion define-macro="confirm-assertion">
      <div id="confirm-assertion" class="yui-module">
	<div class="hd">Confirm CC&empty; Assertion</div>
	<div class="bd">

	    <p>Asserting that a work is free of rights lets others
	    know that they may reuse it without restriction.  Are you
	    certain you wish to do this?
	    </p>

	    <div class="form-row yui-buttongroup">

	      <span class="yui-button">
		<span class="first-child">
		  <button type="submit" id="decline-assertion-submit"
			  name="decline">
		    No, I Do Not Assert
		  </button>
		</span>
	      </span>

	      <span class="yui-button">
		<span class="first-child">
		  <button type="submit" id="confirm-assertion-submit" 
			  name="confirm">
		    I So Assert
		  </button>
		</span>
	      </span>

	    </div>

	</div>
      </div>
</metal:confirm-assertion>

    </div>

    <div id="page-results" class="x-hide-display">

  <div id="results" class="yui-module">
    <div class="hd">CC&empty; Results</div>
    <div class="bd" id="dedication-results">

      <p>Choose which style of button you'd like on your webpage:</p>

      <div class="licensebox" align="center">
	<table>
	  <tr>
	    <td valign="bottom" align="center">
	      <img src="http://labs.creativecommons.org/zero/images/88x31/cc-zero.png"
	      style="border:0px;" /><br/>
	      <input type="radio" name="button" checked
             onclick="swapbutton('http://labs.creativecommons.org/zero/images/88x31/cc-zero.png')"
	      />
	    </td>
	    <td valign="bottom" align="center">
	      <img src="http://labs.creativecommons.org/zero/images/80x15/cc-zero.png"
	      style="border:0px;" /><br/>
	      <input type="radio" name="button"
             onclick="swapbutton('http://labs.creativecommons.org/zero/images/80x15/cc-zero.png')"
	      />
	    </td>

	  </tr>
	</table>
      </div>

      <span id="waiver-results-leadin">
	Here's a preview of how your waiver will appear on your site:
      </span>
      <span id="assertion-results-leadin">
	Here's a preview of how your assertion will appear on your
	site:
      </span>

      <div class="preview" id="results-preview">
      </div>

      <div class="hd" style="margin-top:10px;">What to do next</div>
      <h3>Have a website?</h3>
      <p>Copy the text below to your Web site to let your visitors
      know what license applies to your works.</p> 
      <textarea id="results-html" cols="70" rows="6" onfocus="select()">
      </textarea>
    </div>
    <div class="ft"></div>
  </div>

  <div id="page-bailout" class="x-hide-display">

    <metal:bailout define-macro="post-bailout">
      <div id="bailout" class="yui-module">
	<div class="hd">CC&empty;: Declined</div>
	<div class="bd">
	  <p>What would you like to do next?</p>
	  <ul>
	    <li><a href="./index.html">start over</a></li>
	    <li><a href="http://wiki.creativecommons.org/CcZero">learn more</a></li>
	  </ul>
	</div>
      </div>
    </metal:bailout>

  </div>


    </div>

  </div>
  

</div>
</metal:body>

</body>
</html>
